dict.string: Insert your MicroView and Programmer with Pin 1 in hole C7.
Select your 330Ω resistor and insert it into points A10 and A15 of your breadboard.
Select your Red LED and insert the short leg into point B14 and the long leg into B15 of your breadboard.
Connect your MicroView to your computer’s USB Port.
Click on the “Run on Arduino” to put this code on your MicroView.
